text: Immanuel Ngatjizeko (30 May 1952 - 5 March 2022) was a Namibian politician. He was a member of the SWAPO Party. He was born in Otjohorongo, Namibia. He was a member of the National Assembly from 2000 until 2018. Ngatjizeko was also a member of the Namibian Cabinet from 2005 until 2018 during the Hifikepunye Pohamba and Hage Geingob presidencies. Ngatjizeko died on 5 March 2022 in Windhoek, Namibia at the age of 69. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:2022 deaths Category:SWAPO politicians
